</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Empirical calibrated radiocarbon sampler: a tool for incorporating radiocarbon-date and calibration error into Bayesian phylogenetic analyses of ancient DNA</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Molak%20M"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Martyna Molak</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Martyna Molak</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>School of Biological Sciences, University of Sydney, Sydney, Australia</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Museum and Institute of Zoology, Polish Academy of Sciences, Warsaw, Poland</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Molak%20M"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Martyna Molak</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Suchard%20MA"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>3</sup>Department of Human Genetics, David Geffen School of Medicine at UCLA, University of California, Los Angeles, USA</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>4</sup>Department of Biostatistics, UCLA Fielding School of Public Health, University of California, Los Angeles, USA</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>5</sup>Department of Biomathematics, David Geffen School of Medicine at UCLA, University of California, Los Angeles, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Suchard%20MA"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>3,</sup><sup>4,</sup><sup>5</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ho%20SYW"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Simon Y W Ho</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">Simon Y W Ho</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>School of Biological Sciences, University of Sydney, Sydney, Australia</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ho%20SYW"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Simon Y W Ho</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Beilman%20DW"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">David W Beilman</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3><span class="name western">David W Beilman</span></h3>
<div class="p">
